Class FrcOpenCVDetector<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • frclib.FrcOpenCVDetector<O>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - specifies the type of the detected objects.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    trclib.TrcVisionTask.VisionProcessor<Mat,O>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FrcFaceDetector, FrcVisionTarget

    public abstract class FrcOpenCVDetector<O>
extends java.lang.Object
implements trclib.TrcVisionTask.VisionProcessor<Mat,O>
    This class implements a generic OpenCV detector. Typically, it is extended by a specific detector that provides the algorithm to process an image for detecting objects using OpenCV APIs.
